pageContext.claim: “Nancy Pelosi will go down as the least productive Speaker of the House in history. She is dominated by AOC Plus 3 and the Radical Left. Mexico and Canada, after waiting for 6 months to be approved, are ready to flee - and who can blame them? Too bad!”
pageContext.analysis: Mexico has ratified the revised North American Free Trade Agreement. But contrary to Trump's claim, Canada's Parliament had not yet done so at the time of this statement.
